Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF MONREAL, MUNICIPALITY OF SAN JACINTO, PROVINCE OF MASBATE, TO THAT OF "AGO".
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 702, November 01, 1945 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF MONREAL, MUNICIPALITY OF SAN JACINTO, PROVINCE OF MASBATE, TO THAT OF "AGO".
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in Congress assembled:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of Monreal, in the municipality of San Jacinto, Province of Masbate, is hereby changed to that of "Ago".ℒαwρhi৷
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved, November 1, 1945.
